Job Description
1. Liaise with corporate clients on corporate advisory work, corporate finance, corporate employee benefits, trade finance, Human resources, etc;
2. Source and develop pipeline of corporate clients;
3. Develop and foster relationships with clients, and key stake holders;
4. Working with our partners, such as private equities, family offices and overseas FI.
Compensation
1. $2,400 to $4,000 depending on experience;
2. Opportunity to travel overseas for project management and deals.

